flowchart TD
    A[Client Request] --> B[Fastify Route Handler]
    B --> C{Auth Middleware<br/>JWT Validation}
    C -->|401 Unauthorized| Z1[Reject: 401]
    C -->|Valid Token| D{Tenant Middleware<br/>RLS Set}
    D --> E[K3 executeAction]
    E --> F{K4 Policy Engine<br/>RBAC Permission Check}
    F -->|403 Forbidden| Z2[Reject: 403]
    F -->|Permitted| G[Guardrails Evaluate]

    subgraph Guardrails Layer
        direction TB
        G --> H[Load Active Rules<br/>Matching action_pattern]
        H --> I{For Each Rule}
        I --> J1[input_validation<br/>Check required fields<br/>Check max_length<br/>Check forbidden patterns]
        I --> J2[sensitivity_flag<br/>Check input_contains<br/>Check match_any]
        I --> J3[require_confirmation<br/>Check confirmation_token]
        I --> J4[block<br/>Check condition match]

        J1 -->|Fail| K1[Verdict: BLOCK<br/>Clear Error Message]
        J1 -->|Pass| L[Next Rule]
        J2 -->|Match| K2[Verdict: FLAG<br/>Logged Warning]
        J2 -->|No Match| L
        J3 -->|No Token| K3[Verdict: REQUIRE_CONFIRMATION<br/>Return Token Format]
        J3 -->|Valid Token| L
        J4 -->|Match| K4[Verdict: BLOCK<br/>Explicit Error]
        J4 -->|No Match| L
    end

    K1 --> LOG[Log to guardrail_evaluations]
    K2 --> LOG
    K3 --> LOG
    K4 --> LOG
    L --> M{Final Verdict}

    LOG --> M

    M -->|BLOCK| Z3[Reject: Clear Error<br/>+ Audit Log via K3]
    M -->|REQUIRE_CONFIRMATION| Z4[Return: Confirmation Required<br/>+ Audit Log via K3]
    M -->|FLAG| N[Continue Execution<br/>+ Flag Logged<br/>+ Audit Log via K3]
    M -->|PASS| N

    N --> O[Action Handler Executes]
    O --> P[Audit Log Written<br/>via K3 Pipeline]
    P --> Q[Response to Client]

    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style Z1 fill:#ffcdd2
    style Z2 fill:#ffcdd2
    style Z3 fill:#ffcdd2
    style Z4 fill:#fff3e0
    style K2 fill:#fff9c4
    style N fill:#c8e6c9
    style Q fill:#c8e6c9
    style LOG fill:#e8eaf6
